collection.name: Meta Angels NFT
collection.description:
A collection of 10,000 unique Meta Angels, generated from more than 400 hand drawn elements and stored as ERC-721A tokens on the Ethereum Blockchain.

Our Angels represent the vastness and similarity between us all, spanning the full spectrum of race and gender and showcasing the beauty in diversity. Strong, kind, and generous, they stand for the better world that we build together through our actions. 

Artist: Sarana Haeata

[www.metaangelsnft.com](https://www.metaangelsnft.com)
